{"tid":1675310,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「諗唔到卡尼　點解要過曼聯」","createTime":"2019-10-25T18:45:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T03:01:32.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"43a4fcdc35980ce628e672fbf1b08e9f1f345e4e","tid":1675310,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:45:41.000Z","msg":"前熱刺門將保羅羅賓遜表示，球隊當家射手哈利卡尼，根本不會考慮由熱刺轉會曼聯，因為曼聯的實力及不上熱刺。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯屬英格蘭足球史上，其中一支最成功的球隊，而且紅魔捨得使錢、全球知名度又高，故不少頂級球星都願意加盟。目前紅魔鬼攻力疲弱，前隊長堅尼就希望曼聯，可以購入英格蘭隊長哈利卡尼。<br />\n<br />\n保羅羅賓遜表示：「曼聯一直和卡尼扯上關係，但我看不到為何卡尼要由熱刺轉會曼聯，如果要取得成功甚至獎盃，留在熱刺得到的機會更大。如果有外國球員希望踢英超，當然不介意入魔，曼聯是一間充滿歷史的球會啊。但照目前形勢看，他們現在和以前，差距實在太大了。」(<a href=\"http://goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoal.com&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=cbf5eea6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"f792a06f5b1248061ad176bcab0699e1749cf7d0","tid":1675310,"uid":21969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:51:24.000Z","msg":"郭富城嘅弱？"},{"pid":"46abd32e31d81ecdb64ac10631727c74e0f19148","tid":1675310,"uid":37197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T19:06:52.000Z","msg":"葡萄成熟時？"},{"pid":"31b735ea679d899946ddd44b53fb33263c627e89","tid":1675310,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T02:42:23.000Z","msg":"明年今日？"},{"pid":"c1b98b060bd96a10e76834d2843a7bccc52f00f6","tid":1675310,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T02:49:26.000Z","msg":"馬客尼都過左 有咩諗唔到"},{"pid":"b97466ddf93c69ece9babfe817e0c516d6905f65","tid":1675310,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T02:49:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>馬古尼都過左 有咩諗唔到</blockquote>"},{"pid":"203c0ac558df91a9af642d9dbcc355e7b9efcab3","tid":1675310,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T02:49:57.000Z","msg":"歌詞黎？"},{"pid":"a37ebf050a2e74986e83bb3ab418142eb5ebffa4","tid":1675310,"uid":8733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T02:57:18.000Z","msg":"獌拎獎大機會好多喎 超碼人地有錢"},{"pid":"a191c60153e1b77961a72ebb9bf5472516d0d4e1","tid":1675310,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f792a06f5b1248061ad176bcab0699e1749cf7d0","tid":1675310,"uid":21969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:51:24.000Z","msg":"郭富城嘅弱？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:01:32.000Z","msg":"張國追既榮"}]}